- 1 mark for `Component` abstract class with fields
- 1 mark for `addChild()` and `isLeaf()` methods
- 2 marks for recursive `getRolledUpCost()` with base case + recursion
- 1 mark each for `LeafPart` and `Assembly` (1 × 2 = 2 marks)
- 1 mark for `Serializable`, constructors, abstraction keyword

