C_{\text{sell}} &= 8460.60 \times 1.25 = \text{₹ } 10,575.75
\end{aligned}
$$

**Final answer:** Total effective cost = **₹ 7,170**, Landed cost = **₹ 8,460.60**, Selling price ≈ **₹ 10,576**.

